(25, 'Avenger End Game', '2021', 'Anthony Russo And Joe Russo', 'Action, Adventure, Superhero, Fantasy, Science Fiction', 'avenger.jpg', 'Twenty-three days after Thanos used the Infinity Gauntlet to destroy half of all life in the universe, Carol Danvers rescued Nebula and Tony Stark, who were stranded in outer space after their fight with Thanos. They are joined by Natasha Romanoff, Bruce Banner, Steve Rogers, Rocket, Thor, Pepper Potts, and James Rhodes on Earth. The group finds Thanos on a remote planet and plans to seize and use the Infinity Stones and reverse his actions, but Thanos has destroyed the stones to prevent them from being reused. An enraged Thor finally beheaded Thanos.\r\nFive years later, Scott Lang stepped out of the quantum realm. He goes to the Avengers HQ, where he explains to Romanoff and Rogers that he only spent five hours in the quantum realm, not five years. and he theorizes that the quantum realm could allow them to time travel back in time, the trio ask Stark — who is now raising a daughter, Morgan, with Pepper — that they retrieve the Infinity Stones from the past and use them to reverse Thanos\' actions in the present. Stark rejects the idea for fear of losing Morgan, but relents after contemplating a devastated Peter Parker. Stark works with Banner, who has combined his wits and the Hulk\'s powers, to design a device for time travel. Banner warns that changing the past doesn\'t change the present and that the slightest change can create a different reality. He and Rocket head to Asgard\'s new refugee home in Norway - New Asgard - to recruit Thor, now a fat drunk, desperate for his failure to stop Thanos. In Tokyo, Romanoff recruits Clint Barton, who is now a street fighter after his family disappeared.\r\nBanner, Lang, Rogers, and Stark travel to New York City in 2012. Banner visits the Sanctum Sanctorum and convinces the Ancient One to give him the Time Stone. Rogers manages to retrieve the Mind Stone, but Stark and Lang accidentally allow Loki from 2012 to escape with the Space Stone. Rogers and Stark head to S.H.I.E.L.D. headquarters. in 1970, where Stark took an early version of the Space Stone and met a young Howard Stark while retrieving it, while Rogers retrieved some Pym Particles from Hank Pym to return to the present. Rocket and Thor went to Asgard in 2013, extracting the Reality Stone from Jane Foster and retrieving Thor\'s hammer, Mjolnir. Nebula and Rhodes went to Morag in 2014 and stole the Power Stone before Peter Quill could steal it. Rhodes returns to the present with the Power Stone, but Nebula is knocked unconscious when her cybernetic implant connects with her from the past. Through this relationship, 2014 Thanos learns about his future success and the Avengers\' desire to turn it around. Thanos captured Nebula 2023 and sent Nebula 2014 to the present day to replace it. Barton and Romanoff travel to Vormir, where the guardian of the Soul Stone, the Red Skull, informs them that it can only be retrieved at the expense of someone they love. Romanoff sacrifices himself, and Barton retrieves the Soul Stone.\r\nBack in the present, the Avengers attach the stones to a glove made by Stark, which Banner uses to restore everything Thanos lost. 2014\'s Nebula uses a time machine to bring 2014\'s Thanos and his warship to the present, and attacks the Avengers headquarters, planning to destroy and rebuild the universe with the Infinity Stones. Nebula 2023 convinces Gamora 2014 to betray Thanos and kill Nebula 2014. Stark, Rogers, and Thor battle Thanos but are overwhelmed. Thanos summons his army to destroy Earth, but a returning Stephen Strange arrives with the other wizards, the Avengers, and the missing Guardians of the Galaxy, the armies of Wakanda and Asgard, and the Ravagers to fight Thanos and his army with Danvers, who destroys Thanos\' ship when he arrive. After defeating the heroes, Thanos snatches the gauntlet, but Stark steals the stone and uses it to eliminate Thanos and his Army, then dies from the energy released by the stone.\r\n\r\nAfter Stark\'s funeral, Thor appoints the Valkyrie as ruler of New Asgard and joins the Guardians of the Galaxy, where Quill looks for Gamora 2014. Rogers returns the Infinity Stones and Mjolnir to their respective times and settles in the past to live with Peggy Carter. In the present, the aging Rogers gives Sam Wilson the shield and the name Captain America.'),
(26, 'KKN Di Desa Penari   ', '2022', 'Awi Suryadi', 'Horor', '62a188b4259dfKKN.jpg', 'The mystical story was experienced by six students who carried out Real Work Lectures (KKN) in a remote village. The six students were named Ayu, Nur, Widya, Bima, Anton and Wahyu. The story of KKN in Penari Village is divided into two versions of the story, namely the version of Nur and Widya. So what is the full story of KKN in Nur\'s version of the Dancing Village?\r\nNur is a girl who dreams of studying at the university she has dreamed of since childhood. Month after month he had passed, until finally he arrived at the final semester which required him to complete his community service task or known as KKN.\r\nNur and her six friends had to find a place for KKN on their own because they didn\'t have the opportunity to take part in the KKN that had been determined from the campus. One night, Ayu, a friend from Nur\'s faculty, was just talking about her plan. He already has a suitable place to carry out their KKN activities and Nur will participate in observing the introduction of KKN locations.\r\nNur then prepares for his departure to the village that Ayu is referring to. On the sidelines, Nur remembered that he had to immediately tell his other colleagues. Because KKN is an activity that must be completed together.\r\nThe days passed and it was time for Nur to go to the village which was the location of KKN. Nur also saw the deer car that had stopped, Ayu, her best friend, came out, followed by a man behind her. Nur thought maybe it was Mas Ilham, Ayu\'s older brother who would take them to the KKN location.'),
(27, 'Avenger: Infinity War ', '2018', 'Anthony Russo And Joe Russo', 'Action, Adventure, Superhero, Fantasy, Science Fiction', '62a188bc7d484avenger2.jpeg', 'Avengers: Infinity War has a story related to the previous series of Marvel films. Rows of eternal stones that had appeared in a number of films are now a source of trouble. Thanos (Josh Brolin) has an ambition to collect six immortal stones scattered in various places. Each stone has its own power so not just anyone can get it. If you already have the six immortal stones, Thanos can become the ruler of the universe. Thanos also intends to eliminate half the population of the universe because it is believed to make life more prosperous.\r\nThanos and his men spread terror while looking for these stones. The cruelty of Thanos was witnessed by Bruce Banner/Hulk (Mark Ruffalo) and Thor (Chris Hemsworth). They intend to find another superhero in order to prevent Thanos\' ambitions.\r\nThe Hulk returns to Earth and tells of Thanos\' actions to Tony Stark/Iron Man (Robert Downey Jr.), Doctor Strange (Benedict Cumberbatch) and Wong (Benedict Wong). Unfortunately, Thanos had appeared before they could go any further.\r\nAs a result, Iron Man and Doctor Strange entered Thanos\' starship. The chaos escalates when Peter Parker/Spider-Man (Tom Holland) joins them.\r\nMeanwhile, Thor is saved by members of the Guardians of the Galaxy. Thor believes that he can only save Thanos with the help of his magic hammer. With Rocket (voiced by Bradley Cooper) and Groot (voiced by Vin Diesel), Thor goes to another planet to get a new magic hammer. As Thor and the Hulk devise a plan, Thanos\' henchmen go after Vision (Paul Bettany). One of the immortal stones resides in Vision\'s body. Realizing that her boyfriend\'s life is in danger, Wanda Maximoff/Scarlet Witch (Elizabeth Olsen) asks for the help of Steve Rogers/Captain America (Chris Evans), Natasha Romanoff/Black Widow (Scarlett Johansson), and Sam Wilson/Falcon (Anthony Mackie).\r\nCaptain America then takes them to Wakanda and meets T\'Challa/Black Panther (Chadwick Boseman) and Bucky Barnes/Winter Soldier (Sebastian Stan). Captain America felt Wakanda was a safe place. Wakanda also has sufficient troops to be able to face war.\r\nSo where is Thanos? The villain is forcing his stepdaughter, Gamora (Zoe Saldana) to show her the location of one of the immortal stones. This makes Peter Quill/Star-Lord (Chris Pratt), Drax (Dave Bautista), and Mantis (Pom Klementieff) determined to save him.'),
(28, 'Man Of Steel ', '2013', 'Zack Snyder', 'Action, Superhero, Fantasy, Science Fiction, Adventure', '62a188c824bfaman-of-steel.jpg', 'In the film, Clark Kent or Superman learns that he is a super-powered being from the planet Krypton. He also keeps mankind safe from the attack of General Zod who wants to destroy the earth. The film Man of Steel begins when the planet Krypton experiences destruction which makes Jor-El, the leader of the planet, send his son to Earth. Before being killed by General Zod who is a rebel on Planet Krypton, Kal-El or Superman, played by Henry Cavill, was sent to Earth.\r\nKal-El survives and lands on a farm owned by Jonathan and Martha. Since then Kal-El\'s name has changed to Clark Kent. The couple also cared for Clark Kent into adulthood. But they realized that Clark Kent had extraordinary powers. Of course, because he comes from Planet Krypton, he has super powers that do not exist in ordinary humans.\r\nHowever, they chose to keep Clark Kent\'s advantages a secret from others. One day Jonathan had an accident and died. Clark, who failed to help his father because he was forbidden to use his super powers, was frustrated. He then decided to get out of the area and live a nomadic life to hide who he really was.\r\nOne day, General Zod\'s Krypton spaceship is discovered by the military. Clark, who has the genetic codex from Jor-El, infiltrated the plane and was able to communicate with them. There, Clark first met Lois Lane, the reporter for the Daily Planet newspaper. An accident then forced Clark to use his superpowers to help Lois. Lois was confused, she wanted to write about Clark Kent\'s strangeness in her newspaper but she also wanted to cover it up in order to keep Clark safe, which the military didn\'t want to know.\r\nNot only that, General Zod also intends to take over the earth to turn it into like Planet Krypton.'),
(29, 'Tranformers ', '2017', 'Michael Bay', 'Action, Adventure, Thriller, Science Fivtion', '62a188d21ea56transformers.jpg', 'In AD 484, King Arthur and his knights fought a battle against the Saxons. Meanwhile, Merlin enlists the help of the Knights of Iacon, a group of twelve Transformers who have been hiding on Earth. They give Merlin an alien knight and combine himself with a great dragon to help Arthur win over the Saxons, but before Merlin says that a great evil will one day come for the knight.\r\nNow, three years after the battle in Hong Kong,[N 1] Transformers are declared unlawful by all governments on Earth, with the Transformer Reaction Force (TRF) being formed from the downfall of Cemetery Wind to eradicate alien robots, though more Transformers are arriving constantly- constantly arrived on Earth. . Meanwhile, huge metallic horns began to rise from various parts of the world. In a war-torn part of Chicago, a group of kids find a ship with knights inside before being caught by a TRF drone. Izabella, a survivor of the Battle of Chicago, saves the children along with her Transformers partner Sqweeks and her canopy robot. Due to a drone error, Canopy is killed by the Decepticon before Bumblebee and Cade Yeager (who are also being hunted by TRF) arrive and help the children, Izabella, and Sqweeks escape the drone. While Cade fends off the TRF, Cade finds a robot knight on the ship, which attaches an amulet to his arm. The Decepticon Barricade observed this action and reported the discovery to Megatron. Cade then returns to the junkyard in South Dakota (with Izabella and Sqweeks hitching a ride with him) where the remaining Autobots are hiding from the TRF, including Bumblebee, Hound, Drift, Crosshairs, Wheelie, Grimlock, Slug, Daytrader, Trench, and three Minis. - Dinobots.\r\nIn deep space, Optimus Prime crashes into Cybertron, discovering that the ship is headed straight for Earth. He meets Quintessa, the self-proclaimed creator of Transformers, who uses Optimus\' brain and changes his name to Nemesis Prime. Quintessa tasked him with returning the knights from the robot knights who had stolen from him. He reveals, that Earth is actually Cybertron\'s ancient enemy, Unicron, and he intends to drain his life force using knights, so that Cybertron can be restored.TRF member and former Autobot ally William Lennox moderates the deal between TRF and Megatron so he can find Cade and recover his amulet. In exchange, Megatron demands the release of the members of the Decepticons, including Nitro Zeus, Dreadbot, Mohawk, and Onslaught. Megatron and TRF find Cade, his co-workers Jimmy, Izabella, Sqweeks, and the Autobots thanks to a tracking device planted in Bumblebee while fighting in Chicago. They flee to an abandoned town where they find Bumblebee\'s tracking device. In the ensuing battle, Dreadbot, Onslaught, Mohawk, and several TRF soldiers are killed by Grimlock, Slug, Crosshairs, Drift, and Bumblebee. As a result, Megatron, Nitro Zeus, and Barricade were forced to retreat. While fighting a TRF plane, Cade is approached by Cogman, a Transformer envoy who takes him and Bumblebee to England to meet his master, Sir Edmund Burton. There, Burton arranges a meeting between Cade and Viviane Wembly, an Oxford professor, who has just been kidnapped by Autobot Hot Rod under Burton\'s orders. Burton introduces himself as the last member of the \"Witwiccan\" order, an ancient fraternity dedicated to keeping the Transformers\' history secret on earth. He also reveals that Viviane is Merlin\'s last descendant, and that she must find and use her wand to prevent Cybertron\'s impending destruction of Earth.\r\nAfter escaping the TRF, Barricades, and the police (causing multiple car accidents along the way), Cade, Viviane, Bumblebee, and Cogman follow the clues left by Viviane\'s father and take them to the HMS Alliance museum (after Burton closes the attraction and chases away tourists). ) to sea to find the sunken Cybertronian Knights while the TRF chased them with their own submarine. Burton met with the Prime Minister to engage the military at Stonehenge, which he dedicated was an access point to Unicron. On the ship, Cade and Vivian find the graves of Merlin and his bodyguards. Viviane activated her guards, and the ship rose to the surface. The TRF confronts the group and attempts to take the bodyguards from them before the mind-controlled Optimus forces them to surrender the bodyguards. Bumblebee chases Optimus and the two Autobots fight each other. Before Optimus can kill Bumblebee, the mute Autobot finally speaks, freeing Optimus from Quintessa\'s control. Megatron, revealed to be in cahoots with Quintessa and displeased with Optimus\' failure, arrives to steal the bodyguards and flees while the Knights attack Optimus for his alleged betrayal. Cade stops the Knights with the amulet, which transforms into the sword Excalibur, and the Knights surrender to Cade as the last knight, who then urges Optimus to fight against them for Earth once again.\r\nCybertron establishes itself as an anchor to Earth, Megatron, Nitro Zeus, and Barricade delivering bodyguards to Quintessa, who begins draining Earth\'s life force from Unicron. Burton and the British military intervene, and Megatron shoots Burton, who dies with Cogman at his side. The Autobots arrive to join the fight with TRF, Cade, Viviane, Izabella, and Sqweeks, landing on Cybertron and battling Megatron and Quintessa\'s antagonists, the Infernocons. Defeating their enemy with help from the Knights as dragons, the Autobots reach the room where the staff and Quintessa are. Optimus defeats Megatron by kicking him through the walls of the Ignition Chamber, sending him flying to Earth, while Bumblebee kills Nitro Zeus. Together, Optimus and Bumblebee seem to kill Quintessa. Viviane removes her bodyguard, stopping Earthtron\'s destruction on Earth but leaving the two worlds connected. Optimus states that the humans and Transformers must now work together to rebuild their world, and sends a message calling the surviving Autobots to return home.'),
(30, 'Spider-Man No Way Home ', '2021', 'Jon Watts', 'Action, Comedy, Adventure, Superhero, Science Fiction, Fantasy', '62a188db4e465SpiderMan.jpg', 'Spiderman No Way Home tells about the anxiety of Peter Parker, played by Tom Holland, because he was slandered. Mysterio, played by Jake Gyllenhaal is the one who slandered Parker and finally died before the problem could be solved.'),
(31, 'Jumanji The Next Level ', '2019', 'Jack Kasdan', 'Comedy, Action, Adventure, Fantasy', '62a188f55e5fajumanji.jpg', 'The four main characters of Dwayne \'The Rock\' Johnson, Karen Gillan, Jack Black and Kevin Hart return to the world of Jumanji. They are Smolder Bravestone (The Rock), Franklin Finbar (Hart), Ruby Roundhouse (Gillan) and Professor Sheldon Oberon (Black).\r\nIt\'s just that Spencer (Alex Wolff), Martha (Morgan Turner), Fridge (Ser\'Darius Blain) and Bethany (Madison Iseman) don\'t get the same avatar as in Jumanji: Welcome to the Jungle (2017). Jumanji\'s game console is broken so they can\'t choose an avatar.\r\nMartha, Fridge and Bethany are forced to play Jumanji because Spencer gets sucked in while repairing the game console. Not only the three of them, Spencer\'s grandfather named Eddie (Danny DeVito), and his friend, Milo (Danny Glover), also moved around the universe.\r\nEddie got the avatar Smolder, Milo got the avatar Franklin, Fridge got the avatar Sheldon, Martha got the avatar Ruby and Bethany got the horse character. The weaknesses and strengths of each avatar changed completely from the previous one.\r\nJumanji\'s game guide, Nigel (Rhys Darby), explains that this game is more challenging than ever. Not even all players can leave the game alive as before. Players must now bravely traverse extreme obstacles and return safely from the most dangerous game in the world.\r\nIn addition to several major stars, Jumanji: The Next Level also includes action from Dania Ramirez, Rory McCann, Lamorne Morris and Lucy DeVito in undisclosed roles.\r\nMassi Furlan and Ashley Scott also appear as Renaldo and Ashley, and Bebe Neuwirth will reprise her role as Nora Shepherd from the original film.'),
(32, 'One Punch Man  ', '2015', 'Shingo Natsume', 'Action Fiction, Comedy, Superhero Comics', '62a19823a25e1saitama.jpg', 'The beginning of the story begins with a young man named Saitama. To realize his dream, Saitama worked hard by continuing to practice and study without stopping for three years.\r\nDuring the process of reaching the peak of his dream, Saitama did many things and he was willing to lose his hair to change his appearance to be different. Over time Saitama\'s strength was very strong, even he was able to fight many enemies with just one blow. His strength seemed so incomparable that no one was able to resist. Still in the One Punch Man synopsis, this power has brought him into big trouble.\r\nOn the other hand, he began to lose enthusiasm and no longer enjoyed the thrill of fighting because he was bored.\r\nOne day Saitama\'s monotonous life begins to change after meeting Genos Cyborg (voiced by Kaito Ishikawa).\r\nThe 19-year-old Genos has an interest in Saitama\'s powers and wishes to become his disciple.\r\nThis introduction makes Genos offer Saitama that they both join the Hero Association.\r\nThe association is officially certified and contributes positively to society so that Saitama\'s chances of being widely recognized as a hero are quite promising.\r\nSurprised that he was a lesser-known hero, he quickly accepted Genos\' invitation to join the association.\r\nAfter being declared to join the Hero Association, Saitama seems to start a new journey in facing new swarms of enemies.\r\nThe battle that was originally boring now feels challenging again and Saitama seems to get a new power.'),
(33, 'Kimetsu no Yaiba', '2021', 'Haruo Sotozaki', 'Adventure Fiction, Dark Fantasy, Martial Arts', 'demonslayer.jpg', 'Set in Japan during the Taisho period, Tanjiro Kamado is a kind and intelligent boy who lives with his family and earns money by selling charcoal. Everything changed when his family was attacked and slaughtered by a demon (oni). Tanjiro and his sister Nezuko are the only survivors of the incident, although Nezuko has now turned into a demon but surprisingly she still shows signs of emotion and thinking like a human. Tanjiro then becomes a demon slayer to turn Nezuko back into a human again, and to prevent the tragedy that happened to him and his sister from happening to others.'),
(34, 'Fast &amp; Furious 9 ', '2021', 'Justin Lin', 'Action, Crime Film, Thriller, Adventure', '62a19831ab362Fast&Furious.jpg', 'The film opens with a reverse plot that tells about Dom and Jakob\'s past when they were still mechanics of the Nascar racer who was none other than their father (Jack Toretto). The fateful incident happened to his father when he was competing at speed at the race, the car driven by Jack caught fire in the middle of the race. Dom and Jack were just stunned when they found the incident, it caused deep trauma to both of them.\r\nThen the scene continues where Dom who at that time decided to retire from the world of racing and intelligence. He chose to live in the countryside with his small family. Trouble arises when former teammate Roman Pearce (Tyrese Gibson) visits Dom\'s house to ask him and his wife Lett (Michelle Rodriguez) to go on a mission.\r\nOn this mission, Dom and Letty are asked to find Mr Nobody\'s plane carrying Cipher (Charlize Theron) that crashed. There is a super-advanced device called Ares that fell with the cipher at that time. Apparently, Dom\'s journey to find cipher and Ares did not go smoothly. Because they are not the only ones who want these sophisticated tools. This is where the iconic side of FF (Fast Furious) which always uses super-fast cars with super-advanced technology is shown. The chase scene was inevitable. In the midst of the chase, Dom saw a familiar figure in his life, that figure was Jakob\'s younger brother. The scene changes when Dom finds out who is behind his father\'s tragic accident, Jakob is the person responsible for sabotaging the car that caused his father\'s death. Dom finds out after he is imprisoned for hitting a racing rival and crashing his father\'s car. There is a unique scene in this FF9 series, where one of the characters named Han (Sun Kang) who was declared dead in the previous series now comes and joins to help Dom on this mission.\r\nIn FF9, Han is shown to have reached an advanced age and already has an adopted daughter who is the biological child of two Ares technology inventors.');

